premise_source_doc_sentence: The album did produce four singles with two top 40 singles , however , `` Never Leave Me Alone '' , which was released on October 22 , 1996 through Death Row Records and peaked at number 33 on the Billboard Hot 100 `` Nobody Does It Better '' , which became his biggest hit as a solo artist , peaking at number 18 on the Hot 100 , `` These Days '' , released through Death Row Records and `` I Do n't Wan na Hurt No More '' , released in 1998 through Breakaway .
